headline: Office occupiers eye workplace experience improvement strategies to boost office attendance: CBRE
summary: While most companies pointed to a lack of mandated policies or enforcement as a barrier to increasing in-office attendance, “more is needed than just policies,” according to a report.

headline: CBRE Group Completes Turner & Townsend/Project Management Combination; Vincent Clancy Joins CBRE Board of Directors
summary: DALLAS, January 03, 2025--CBRE Group, Inc. (NYSE:CBRE) today announced that it has completed its plan to combine its project management business with Turner & Townsend, its majority-owned subsidiary, and that Vincent Clancy, Board chair and chief executive officer of Turner & Townsend, has joined CBRE’s Board of Directors.
